				</common:classification>
			</classificationInformation>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Multi-Si ingot is a high-performance multi-crystalline silicon used in silicon nitride crucibles. It has comparable oxygen distribution to ingots grown in silica crucibles, but with lower carbon levels. It is used in the production of conventional crystalline silicon solar cells. The quality of multi-crystalline silicon ingot can be improved by adding an additional graphite layer on the hot-zone of directional solidification furnace.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">多晶硅锭是一种用于氮化硅坩埚的高性能多晶硅。它的氧分布与在二氧化硅坩埚中生长的硅锭相当，但碳含量较低。它可用于生产传统的晶体硅太阳能电池。通过在定向凝固炉的热区添加额外的石墨层，可以提高多晶硅锭的质量。</common:generalComment>
